{"tid":1108704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爸爸丟掉兒子12箱色情影碟AV珍藏　兒子憤怒告父母索償67萬元賠償","createTime":"2019-04-16T05:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T07:12:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9b615973daef09a7d888b0f3fa818f6ab8c77931","tid":1108704,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T05:59:06.000Z","msg":"美國一對父子近日對簿公堂，為的是12箱色情影片光碟。兒子發現12箱珍藏已久的色情影碟被爸爸丟掉，一怒之下向爸爸提告，更向法官指要求爸爸賠償8.6萬美元(約67萬港元)。<br />\n據abcNews 報道，一名美國密西根州男子控告其父母，指控二人將他的色情影碟珍藏丟掉，事源2016年10月，該名男子離婚後搬回父母家中暫住。當時男子安頓好所有事後，他拜託父母將他的物品幫忙寄送至新住所，後來男子發現行李中少了12箱色情影碟，他頓時感到晴天霹靂。<br />\n據法院文件指出，男子的父母向他承認丟掉了其色情影碟珍藏。當時男子曾因事件傳送電郵給父母，並憤怒地說：<br />\n&quot;如果你們對我的私人物品有意見，你們應該直接對我說。否則，你們應該收聲。&quot;<br />\n事後其父親亦有回覆兒子電郵：<br />\n&quot;你信不信都好，我銷毀你的色情影碟是為了你的心靈和情緒健康著想！希望你有一天會明白！&quot;<br />\n據男子表示，12箱的色情影碟中有不少是已絕版或超稀有的影片，估計合共價值逾2.9萬美金(約22.6萬港元)。男子不接受父母的解釋，並要求父母賠償8.6萬美元(約67萬港元)。案件仍在審理中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2325000/2326149/AV_thumb_20190415_J_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2325000%2F2326149%2FAV_thumb_20190415_J_1024.jpg&h=bf263293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2326149/%E7%88%B8%E7%88%B8%E4%B8%9F%E6%8E%89%E5%85%92%E5%AD%9012%E7%AE%B1%E8%89%B2%E6%83%85%E5%BD%B1%E7%A2%9FAV%E7%8F%8D%E8%97%8F%E3%80%80%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E6%86%A4%E6%80%92%E5%91%8A%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F67%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2326149%2F%25E7%2588%25B8%25E7%2588%25B8%25E4%25B8%259F%25E6%258E%2589%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%259012%25E7%25AE%25B1%25E8%2589%25B2%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%25A2%259FAV%25E7%258F%258D%25E8%2597%258F%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2586%25A4%25E6%2580%2592%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%2588%25B6%25E6%25AF%258D%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%2584%259F67%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E8%25B3%25A0%25E5%2584%259F%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCdzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=b22cd6dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2326149/%E7%88%B8%E7%88%B8%E4%B8%9F%E6%8E%89%E5%85%92%E5%AD%9012%E7%AE%B1%E8%89%B2%E6%83%85%E5%BD%B1%E7%A2%9FAV%E7%8F%8D%E8%97%8F%E3%80%80%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E6%86%A4%E6%80%92%E5%91%8A%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F67%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"ce3b3204de7ec48939ababbebd4bfb44227b8251","tid":1108704,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:16:27.000Z","msg":"一早擺上電腦同cloud咪無事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9294def9cebcfca5ef20647788dace401532bff","tid":1108704,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:24:59.000Z","msg":"對仆街父母抵撚死啦，亂掉人啲嘢"},{"pid":"fa919e173882579fc0e330c816554a4a546b96d1","tid":1108704,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9294def9cebcfca5ef20647788dace401532bff","tid":1108704,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:24:59.000Z","msg":"對仆街父母抵撚死啦，亂掉人啲嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:12:43.000Z","msg":"勁過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}